data.description: This LIKE NEW three-bedroom, two-bathroom home features an open living area concept with a kitchen island that opens up to the living room, perfect for entertaining! Kitchen features beautiful granite counter tops and dark cabinetry with tons of recessed lighting and ceramic tile floors. The spacious master suite is located separate from the other two bedrooms. The master bathroom features a large shower, plenty of vanity space, ceramic tile flooring, and a walk-in closet. The generous and maintained backyard features a covered patio and privacy fence. This smart home is equipped with a security system. Take advantage of the abundance of neighborhood amenities the Yowell Ranch Subdivision has to offer to include a community pool, park, walking trails, and basketball court. All appliances convey.
